Computer Graphics Virus

File organization:
	Headerfiles are in the include directory
	Running make creates the executable as virus 

Glui Interface:
	The are two rollout menus containing spinners to adjust the model:
	1	Dimensions  - changes body part sizes
	2	Angles  - moves the body parts in relation to each other

User Input:
	Keys:
		o/p - changes the view to either orthogonal or perspective	
		up/down - zooms in and out (note that this will throw you into perspective mode)
	Mouse:
		left click and drag - changes the eye location along horizontal plane
		right click and drag - rotates view point
